request.description:
Returns the current user and their onboarding status.
Called by the frontend on every app load to rehydrate session.

**Returns**
```json
{
  "user": { "id", "email", "role", "status" },
  "onboarding": {
    "status": "IN_PROGRESS",
    "currentStep": 5
  },
  "profile": {
    "exists": false,
    "completionPercent": 0
  }
}
```

🔒 Requires `Authorization: Bearer {{ACCESS_TOKEN}}`

